com.flamingOctoIronman
This is the top level package for the game.
com.flamingOctoIronman.core
Provides the core classes to start the game.
com.flamingOctoIronman.core.event  
com.flamingOctoIronman.core.manager
Provides com.flamingOctoIronman.core.manager.CoreManger classes for the subsystem level, and a CoreManagerManager to handle them.
com.flamingOctoIronman.framework
Similar to libraries, this provides abstract classes to perform common tasks throughout the game.
com.flamingOctoIronman.framework.event
This package is a framework for handles events.
com.flamingOctoIronman.framework.manager
This class houses the framework for making Managers and controlling them via ManagerMangers.
com.flamingOctoIronman.library
Contains all the classes for the game's library level.
com.flamingOctoIronman.library.math
The math library.
com.flamingOctoIronman.library.math.matrix
Contains the Marix math classes, and a Matrix class to hold matrices.
com.flamingOctoIronman.library.math.vector
Contains the Vector math classes, and a Vector class to hold vectors.
com.flamingOctoIronman.subsystem
Provides the subsystems for the game.
com.flamingOctoIronman.subsystem.debugging
The purpose of this package is to provide a system for debugging.
com.flamingOctoIronman.subsystem.HID
This package allows for the connection to human interface devices.
com.flamingOctoIronman.subsystem.HID.inputEvents
This packages provides InputEvents and an InputEventBusService for handling keyboard and mouse events.
